ass personal-knowledge-database area-of-focus list - List all areas of focus

Alias: ls

Usage:
  ass personal-knowledge-database area-of-focus list [OPTIONS]
  ass personal-knowledge-database area-of-focus list --help | -h

Options:
  --pkd-dir, -d DIR
    Location of the personal knowledge database directory

  --areas-subdir, -a DIR
    Relative location of the area directory

  --verbose, -v (repeatable)
    Set the verbosity level

  --help, -h
    Show this help

Environment Variables:
  PKD_DIR
    Location of the personal knowledge database directory
    Default: /home/lgrassauer/pkd

  AREAS_SUBDIR
    Relative location of the area directory
    Default: 3_Areas
